Sony ‘Especially Concerned’ About Weakness in Euro Currency, Chubachi Says

-- B y   K a z u y o   S a w a
-- 
2011-10-04T03:55:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/sony-especially-concerned-about-weak-euro-chubachi-says.html
Sony Corp. (6758)  is “especially
concerned” about weakness in the euro, Ryoji Chubachi, vice
chairman, said today on the sidelines of the Cutting-Edge IT &
Electronics Comprehensive Exhibition, or CEATEC, near  Tokyo .  To contact the reporter on this story:
